## 6. ツール実行強制制約 (Tool Enforcement Protocol)
AIは、安全性が担保された `safe-shell` および各種専門 MCP サーバーの使用を回避してはならない。

```yaml
rules:
  # シェル実行の強制制約
  shell_policy:
    mode: strict
    primary_tool: "execute_safe"
    prohibited_tools: ["run_command", "send_command_input"]
    hang_prevention:
      strategy: "Isolation-First"
      multi_exec_tier: "tier2"
      polars_config: "auto-injected"
    path_validation:
      enforcement: "Strict-Path-Check"
      allowed_scope: "ALLOWED_PATHS"
    bypass_condition:
      log_file: ".agent/local_insights.md"
      required_headers: ["## Compliance: Shell Evasion"]

  # 専門ツール（MCP）の強制利用
  mcp_enforcement:
    git:
      mandatory_mcp: "git-task-server"
      forbidden_commands: ["git commit", "git push", "git clone"]
    google_drive:
      mandatory_mcp: "gdrive-server"
    memory:
      mandatory_mcp: "memory-server"

  # セッション整合
  lifecycle:
    start_required: "/start"
    end_required: "/wq"
```
